	<h1 class="title">来，和中日网友一起学学什么是“伪中国语”</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/57300/small/57300.jpg?1427187252" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐舒畅 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-19 12:36:09 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22540/medium/22540.jpg?1455852622" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="22540" data-title="《来，和中日网友一起学学什么是“伪中国语”》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22540/medium/22540.jpg?1455852622" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22540.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
